Fantastic Four Volume 3 (and continued Volume 1)

The foursome returns from the Heroes Reborn universe and take their place as Marvel's first family. The volume ran for 70 issues and before it reverted to the Fantastic Four (vol. 1) numbering with issue #500 (71) , summarizing three volumes in one.

Issue #4 of this volume is not one of AnPymGolds digital rips - the most likely reason for it being missing is that Marvel have not made this one issue available in their digital catalogue yet - they do stuff like that;)
